OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FLandmark changes to parental leave
OL,7,Fwill be laid out in Parliament on
OL,8,FMonday, allowing parents more rights
OL,9,Ffrom their first day in a new job.
OL,11,FThe reforms to parental leave, part of
OL,12,FLabour's flagship workers' rights
OL,13,Fpackage, include unpaid parental leave
OL,14,Ffrom the first day in a new job, which
OL,15,Fthe government says will give an
OL,16,Fadditional 1.5 million parents
OL,17,Fincreased flexibility to share
OL,18,Fchildcare responsibilities.
