OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FThe sounds of cheers rang out in the
OL,7,FHouse of Commons last December when
OL,8,Fthe government's landmark Employment
OL,9,FRights Bill became law. It applies to
OL,10,FEngland, Scotland, and Wales, but not
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,FAs well as parental reforms, the Act
OL,14,Fincludes an expansion of bereavement
OL,15,Fleave, the right to statutory sick pay
OL,16,Ffrom day one of employment, a ban on
OL,17,Fzero-hour contracts, and a right to
OL,18,Fguaranteed hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
