OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FThere are also protections for
OL,7,Fwhistleblowers who report sexual
OL,8,Fharassment and some trade union and
OL,9,Findustrial action reforms to modernise
OL,10,Flegislation.
OL,12,FThe government previously abandoned
OL,13,Fworkers' rights against unfair
OL,14,Fdismissal from day one in a bid to get
OL,15,Fthe legislation through Parliament. It
OL,16,Fnow intends to introduce the right
OL,17,Fafter six months of service instead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
