OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FIn a statement, Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,7,F"The changes we're bringing in will
OL,8,Fmean every new parent can properly
OL,9,Ftake time off when they have a child,
OL,10,Fand no one is forced to work while ill
OL,11,Fjust to make ends meet.
OL,13,F"This is about giving working families
OL,14,Fthe support they need to balance work,
OL,15,Fhealth and the cost of living...
OL,17,F"Stronger sick pay, parental leave
OL,18,Ffrom day one, and protections that put
OL,19,Fdignity back at the heart of work."
