OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FThe bill was largely welcomed by trade
OL,7,Funions and campaigners, but critics
OL,8,Fargued it will add more financial
OL,9,Fburdens to businesses already
OL,10,Fstruggling with the rise in employers'
OL,11,Fnational insurance.
OL,13,FHere, we look at the new parental
OL,14,Frights reforms.
OL,16,FPaternity leave
OL,18,FFrom April, dads will get the right to
OL,19,Fpaternity leave from day one on the
OL,20,Fjob, as a mother would with maternity
OL,21,Fleave.
