OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FPreviously, they had to have worked
OL,7,Ffor their employer for 26 weeks before
OL,8,Fthey would become eligible.
OL,10,FThe government says this change will
OL,11,Fmean parents will "no longer be forced
OL,12,Fto make the heart-wrenching choice
OL,13,Fbetween being there for the first
OL,14,Fweeks of their child's life or going
OL,15,Fback to work to avoid losing their
OL,16,Fjob".
OL,18,FParental leave rights from day one
