OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FAll parents will now become eligible
OL,7,Ffor unpaid parental leave from day one
OL,8,Fof employment.
OL,10,FPreviously, they would have to work
OL,11,Ffor a year before they were eligible
OL,12,Ffor unpaid parental leave. It meant
OL,13,Fthey would lose any right to time off
OL,14,Fif they left their job to work for a
OL,15,Fnew employer.
OL,17,FIt comes as the government continues
OL,18,Fits parental leave and pay review,
OL,19,Fwhich ministers say is assessing the
OL,20,Fentire system to see how it can work
OL,21,Fbetter for parents and employers.
