OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FExpanded bereavement leave
OL,8,FBereaved partners will now be entitled
OL,9,Fto further rights to paternity leave
OL,10,Ffrom April under separate new laws,
OL,11,Ffollowing campaigning.
OL,13,FIt means that any fathers whose
OL,14,Fpartner dies before their child's
OL,15,Ffirst birthday will now be eligible
OL,16,Ffor up to 52 weeks of leave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
