OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FPreviously, they had no automatic
OL,7,Fright to paternity or parental leave,
OL,8,Feven if they became the sole carer of
OL,9,Ftheir young child and had to rely on
OL,10,Fthe compassion of their employer.
OL,12,FAccording to the Department for
OL,13,FBusiness and Trade (DBT), around
OL,14,F390,000 people who want a job -
OL,15,Fincluding parents - are estimated to
OL,16,Fbe out of work due to their caring
OL,17,Fresponsibilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
