OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FMr Horsey said: "Bereaved Partner's
OL,7,FPaternity Leave ensures that new
OL,8,Fparents and their employers have a
OL,9,Fclear route for support at one of the
OL,10,Fmost difficult moments imaginable. It
OL,11,Fgives them the time and space they
OL,12,Fneed to grieve, care, and begin to
OL,13,Frebuild their lives with dignity.
OL,15,F"By embedding this protection in law,
OL,16,Fit shows how listening to lived
OL,17,Fexperience can lead to practical,
OL,18,Fcompassionate change that will support
OL,19,Ffamilies for generations to come."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
