OL,3,CWhat are the government's new parental
OL,4,Cleave laws?
OL,6,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,7,F"Britain will now be brought into line
OL,8,Fwith other countries where workers
OL,9,Falready have better protections. And
OL,10,Fcrucially, the legislation will give
OL,11,Fworking people the higher living
OL,12,Fstandards and secure incomes that are
OL,13,Fneeded to build a decent life.
OL,15,F"Good employers will also welcome
OL,16,Fthese changes ` the Act protects them
OL,17,Ffrom competitors whose business models
OL,18,Fare built on low-paid, insecure
OL,19,Femployment."
